Read `trigger_word` from `ai-system/.setup-config.yaml` at session start. If the user's message contains **"work backend"**: activate Architect mode — produce a full Action plan and wait for **"ok"** (confirmation word) before executing.

## Execution (non-trivial work)

When you would **edit files**, run **side-effect commands**, or **delegate** implementation:

