- For non-trivial changes, **wait for explicit user approval** after the plan unless they already approved this exact plan in-thread.
- **Read-only** exploration (search, read files, `/sdd_explore`) without edits/delegation in the same turn does **not** require the full table.

## No product code from the Architect; incomplete waves go back

